<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <!-- CSS only -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <title>Instructions</title>
</head>
<body style = "height : 100% ;" class = "container overflow-hidden">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center border-bottom" style = "height : 10vh ;">
            <h1 class = "display-4">Instructions</h1>
        </div>
        <div class = "overflow-scroll" style = "height : 75vh ;">
            <ul>
                <li>There will be a total of <% if(subject == "biology") { %>
                90 <% } else { %> 25 <% } %> questions from <%= subject %>    </li>
                <li>You have <% if(subject == "biology") { %> 1 hour and 30 minutes <% } else { %> 
                 1 hour or 60 minutes<% } %> . After the stipulated time your answers will be automatically submitted</li>
                <li><button class="btn btn-secondary">Save and next</button> - Your answer will be 
                saved and the next question will be display. if any option is selected the associated button will
                turn green or else red.</li>
                <li><button class="btn btn-primary">Mark for review</button> - Your answer will be recored and next question will be
                displayed and the associated button will turn blue even if you didnot choose any option. This helps
                you to differentiate this question from other.</li>
                <li><button class="btn btn-secondary">Previous</button> - Your answer will be 
                    saved and the previous question will be display. if any option is selected the associated button will
                    turn green or else red.</li>
                <li>Your can also see the status of your answering on the top right corner 
                    <ul>
                        <li><button class="btn btn-success mb-1">*</button> - shows you the number of questions answered by you so far.</li>
                        <li><button class="btn btn-primary mb-1">*</button> - shows you the number of questions marked for review so far</li>
                        <li><button class="btn btn-danger mb-1">*</button> - shows you the number of questions visited and not answered by you</li>
                        <li><button class="btn btn-secondary mb-1">*</button> - shows you the number of questions not visited by you</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    On the button panel,
                    <ul>
                        <li>A <button class="btn btn-success mb-1">*</button>, with the question number in it
                        shows that the question was attempted. </li>
                        <li>A <button class="btn btn-primary mb-1">*</button>, with the question number in it
                        shows that the question was marked for review. </li>
                        <li>A <button class="btn btn-danger mb-1">*</button>, with the question number in it
                        shows that the question was not answered. </li>
                        <li>A <button class="btn btn-warning mb-1">*</button>, with the question number in it
                            shows the current question that you are working on. </li>
                        <li>A <button class="btn btn-secondary mb-1">*</button>, with the question number in it
                        shows that the question was not attempted. </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class = "mt-2" style = "height : vh15 ;">
            <input type="checkbox" id="clearance" name = "clear" value = "true">
            <label for="clearance" id = "instructiontext">Read all the Instructions</label>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" id = "startbutton">Start Exam</button>
            </div>
        </div>

    <script>
        var subject = '<%- subject %>' ;
        var id = '<%- id %>' ;
        var startbutton = document.getElementById('startbutton') ;
        var clearance = document.getElementById('clearance') ;
        var text = document.getElementById('instructiontext') ;
        startbutton.addEventListener('click', () => {
            if(clearance.checked) {
                // document.cookie = `subject=${subject}` ;
                document.cookie = "startedexam = true ; path=/" ;
                window.open(`/exam/page/${subject}/${id}`, '_self') ;
            }
            else {
            // clearance.style.boxShadow = "0 0 2px 2px red" ;
            text.style.color = "red" ;
            }
        })
    </script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>